        },
        "score": 0.03306010928961749
      },
      {
        "content": "Unchecked low-level call return value masks failed transfer\n\nA withdrawal uses address.call{value:amount}('') but does not check the boolean success return. On failure the contract continues as if the payout succeeded, corrupting accounting. Equivalent issue with token.transfer returning false (non-reverting tokens). Fix: require(success) on low-level calls and use SafeERC20.",
